Created attachment 33458
A big json document to show the behaviour

I think this "big" json document shows the same distortions when used in a http sampler as post data.

It is generated with the following python code:

import json
d={}
for j in range(50,100):
    for k in range(1,50):
        d['j'*j+'k'*k] = 'k' * j
print json.dumps(d)
